This is the README for ngs.plot: An easy-to-use visualization tool for global enrichment of next-generation sequencing data.

The command options can be displayed when you type the program name without any argument. 

There are some toy examples for you to run through the pipeline under the "example" folder. Please also read "example/README.txt".

For installation and detailed usage, please refer to our online manual: https://code.google.com/p/ngsplot/

